<h3>Is roaming good for field teams and NGOs?</h3>
<p>Yes, it can be useful for field teams, NGOs, mobile clinics, surveys, training sites, and temporary offices if the package supports roaming and the team has a clear setup and power plan.</p>

<h3>Will roaming speeds be the same in every location?</h3>
